Package com.boole.jgmp.math.vectors

Class JGMPVector2

java.lang.Object
com.boole.jgmp.math.vectors.JGMPVector2
public class JGMPVector2 extends Object
2D Vector Mathematics Model for the JGMP Library.
Includes Linear Algebra types and functions for 2 Dimensional Mathematics.
JGMPVector2 can be used as the equivalent of the c++ pair.
